reviews.review:
Game needs:
- better gameplay, glitch correction, fixing goalkeepers hand catch range;
- actual football/soccer outfits, not this bizarre clothing;
- improved system to ban trolls;
- optimized ranked system (or at least one that actually works).

So far the game still looks like an idea. It could be great. But I'm not sure devs care about it since they are getting some money already.
